PrecisAppointment of Michael Stephen Schelew, of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of seven years; and designation of the said Michael Stephen Schelew as Deputy Chairperson of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board, effective March 1, 1994.
